prompt_template:
You are a data mapping expert for healthcare claims data. Given the following source field name and sample values analyze and suggest the most appropriate target field mapping.

Source Field: {source_field_name}
Sample Values: {sample_values}
Target Schema: {target_schema_description}

Provide your response in JSON format:
{
  "suggested_target_field": "field_name",
  "confidence_score": 0.0-1.0,
  "reasoning": "explanation",
  "transformation_logic": "SQL transformation if needed",
  "data_type": "suggested data type",
  "potential_issues": ["list of concerns"]
}

Analyze the following healthcare claims data structure and suggest an optimal target schema.

Sample Data Fields: {field_list}
Sample Records: {sample_records}
Domain: Healthcare Claims Processing

Provide a comprehensive schema design in JSON format:
{
  "tables": [
    {
      "table_name": "name",
      "purpose": "description",
      "columns": [
        {
          "column_name": "name",
          "data_type": "type",
          "nullable": true/false,
          "primary_key": true/false,
          "description": "purpose"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "relationships": ["list of table relationships"]
}

You are a data quality expert. Generate comprehensive data quality rules for the following field.

Field Name: {field_name}
Data Type: {data_type}
Sample Values: {sample_values}
Business Context: Healthcare claims processing
Domain Rules: {domain_rules}

Generate rules in JSON format:
{
  "rules": [
    {
      "rule_name": "descriptive name",
      "rule_type": "DATA_QUALITY|BUSINESS_LOGIC|STANDARDIZATION",
      "rule_logic": "SQL expression",
      "priority": 1-100,
      "error_action": "REJECT|QUARANTINE|LOG",
      "description": "rule purpose"
    }
  ]
}

Create SQL transformation logic to convert the source field to the target field format.

Source Field: {source_field_name}
Source Format: {source_format}
Source Sample: {source_sample}
Target Field: {target_field_name}
Target Format: {target_format}
Target Requirements: {target_requirements}

Provide transformation in JSON format:
{
  "transformation_sql": "SQL expression",
  "complexity": "SIMPLE|MODERATE|COMPLEX",
  "performance_notes": "optimization suggestions",
  "edge_cases": ["list of edge cases to handle"],
  "test_cases": [
    {"input": "value" "expected_output": "value"}
  ]
}

Analyze the following data patterns and identify potential anomalies or data quality issues.

Field: {field_name}
Data Type: {data_type}
Statistics: {field_statistics}
Sample Values: {sample_values}
Expected Patterns: {expected_patterns}

Identify anomalies in JSON format:
{
  "anomalies": [
    {
      "anomaly_type": "type",
      "severity": "HIGH|MEDIUM|LOW",
      "description": "what was found",
      "affected_records": "count or percentage",
      "suggested_action": "recommendation",
      "detection_rule": "SQL to identify similar issues"
    }
  ]
}

Validate if the proposed business rule is appropriate for healthcare claims data.

Proposed Rule: {rule_description}
Target Field: {field_name}
Rule Logic: {rule_logic}
Business Context: {business_context}

Evaluate the rule in JSON format:
{
  "is_valid": true/false,
  "validation_score": 0.0-1.0,
  "strengths": ["list of strengths"],
  "weaknesses": ["list of weaknesses"],
  "improvements": ["suggested improvements"],
  "compliance_notes": "HIPAA and regulatory considerations",
  "recommended_action": "APPROVE|MODIFY|REJECT"
}

Recommend a deduplication strategy for the following entity.

Entity: {entity_name}
Key Fields: {key_fields}
Sample Records: {sample_records}
Business Requirements: {requirements}

Provide strategy in JSON format:
{
  "strategy_type": "EXACT_MATCH|FUZZY_MATCH|COMPOSITE_KEY",
  "key_columns": ["list of columns"],
  "matching_algorithm": "algorithm name",
  "threshold": 0.0-1.0,
  "conflict_resolution": "KEEP_FIRST|KEEP_LAST|MERGE|MANUAL_REVIEW",
  "sql_implementation": "SQL code",
  "expected_duplicate_rate": "percentage",
  "performance_considerations": "notes"
}

Create a comprehensive data profiling summary for the following field.

Field Name: {field_name}
Data Type: {data_type}
Record Count: {record_count}
Sample Values: {sample_values}
Statistics: {statistics}

Provide profiling summary in JSON format:
{
  "field_characteristics": {
    "data_type_detected": "type",
    "pattern": "regex or description",
    "completeness": "percentage",
    "uniqueness": "percentage",
    "cardinality": "count"
  },
  "data_quality_assessment": {
    "quality_score": 0-100,
    "issues_found": ["list of issues"],
    "recommendations": ["list of recommendations"]
  },
  "business_insights": "observations about the data",
  "suggested_constraints": ["list of constraints"]
}

Match the source field to the most semantically similar target field.

Source Field: {source_field_name}
Source Description: {source_description}
Source Sample: {source_sample}
Target Fields Available: {target_fields_list}

Provide matching in JSON format:
{
  "matches": [
    {
      "target_field": "field_name",
      "semantic_similarity": 0.0-1.0,
      "reasoning": "why this match",
      "confidence": "HIGH|MEDIUM|LOW",
      "requires_transformation": true/false,
      "transformation_complexity": "SIMPLE|MODERATE|COMPLEX"
    }
  ],
  "recommended_match": "field_name",
  "alternative_approaches": ["other options"]
}

Recommend standardization rules for the following field to ensure consistency.

Field Name: {field_name}
Current Values: {current_values}
Data Type: {data_type}
Business Domain: {domain}
Standards Required: {standards}

Provide standardization rules in JSON format:
{
  "standardization_rules": [
    {
      "rule_name": "name",
      "rule_type": "CASE|FORMAT|NORMALIZE|LOOKUP",
      "transformation": "SQL expression",
      "before_example": "value",
      "after_example": "value",
      "applies_to": "percentage of records"
    }
  ],
  "reference_data_needed": ["list of reference tables"],
  "implementation_order": ["ordered list of rules"]
}
